talk_abnor_11103_8.kr: 우리 팀은 그렇지 않다는 걸 보여드려야겠습니다만.
talk_abnor_11103_8.en: Our team won't go down so easy, Sam!

talk_alicia_16502_10.kr: ZUXX님은 수갑을 차고 있어서 안전합니다. 걱정할 건 없어요.
talk_alicia_16502_10.en: ZUXX has his handcuffs on, so don't worry!

talk_alicia_16502_12.en: You are safe by an 82% chance! I assure you!

talk_alicia_16502_2.kr: 당신이 도망갈 확률은 그러니까 3% 미만! 문제 없어요!
talk_alicia_16502_2.en: Your chances of getting away are less than 3%! So don't even think of it!

talk_ami_1.en: You always had a good taste for talent, Master!

talk_ami_10.kr:
돌파 필살기로 수비진을 뚫을 수 있어!
신호를 주면 필살기를 쓸게!
talk_ami_10.en:
I can penetrate their lines with my Special Skill! 
Whenever you're ready, Noa!

talk_ami_11.kr: 적이 체력이 다하면 수비라인이 무너져 잊지마!
talk_ami_11.en: Their line of defense will fall when they run out of HP!

talk_ami_12.kr:
이기려면 돌파 등으로
상대 체력을 고갈시키면 돼!
talk_ami_12.en:
Make them run out of HP! 
That's the key to winning the game!

talk_ami_13.kr: 체력이 고갈돼 쓰러진 상대는 잠시 후에 일어나.
talk_ami_13.en: Players that run out of HP come back up in a few moments!

talk_ami_14.kr: 이 경기 흐름에서 이득을 취해야 해

talk_ami_15.kr: 갤럭시 리그는 엄청난 육체적 에너지를 컨트롤하는 경기야
talk_ami_15.en: The Galaxy League is all about power and skills!

talk_ami_16.en: This is a minor bump compared to whats allowed in the League!

talk_ami_17.en: You might want to get used to it.

talk_ami_17103_2_2.kr: 마, 마왕님을 쓰러뜨린 건가요!? 우리 팀이요?
talk_ami_17103_2_2.en: Is this true? Did we really defeat the Demon King of Hellion?

talk_ami_17103_2_4.kr: 그럴 리가요! 지금 아미의 주인님은 이브님 뿐!
talk_ami_17103_2_4.en: Yeah, but I serve Eve now!

talk_ami_17103_2_5.kr: 하지만 모든 패권을 장악했던 비토스님이 이렇게…. 놀랍고 두렵네요.
talk_ami_17103_2_5.en: But I'm surprised you've become victorious over Vitos.

talk_ami_17103_2_6.en: You Humans are starting to frighten me!

talk_ami_19.kr: 주인님 인간이 이제야 뭔가 관심을 주네요!
talk_ami_19.en: Now she seems interested to our offer, Master!

talk_ami_2.kr: 왠지 그 말 10번은 들은 거 같은데…
talk_ami_2.en: That's the 10th time you've said that...

talk_ami_3.kr:
아, 아니요. 앗! 저기 소동이 일어났어요.
축구장 쪽이에요.
talk_ami_3.en:
Ah, nothing. Oh, look! There's something going on at the 
soccer field!

talk_ami_4.en: Master's got her game face on!

talk_ami_7.kr: 난 어른들 놀리는 게 젤 좋더라 히히힛

talk_ami_8.kr:
액션바가 가득 차면 공이 있던 없던 기회가 와!
그 기회를 꼭 잡아!
talk_ami_8.en:
See that Action Bar? When it fills up, you'll get your chance to move! 
With or without the ball! Don't miss it!

talk_ami_9.kr:
기본 리그 매치는 데스매치!
한골만 먹혀도 게임에서 져 버린다구!
talk_ami_9.en:
League Matches are basically Death Matches. 
One goal, and the game is over!

talk_anael_12903_11.kr: 이 우주의 정의는 우리가 지켜낼 것이다. 너흰 그저 우리의 축복을 기다리면 된다.
talk_anael_12903_11.en: We are the ones to secure justice in the universe. All you puny Humans have to do is to wait for our blessing!

talk_anael_12903_13.en: Foolish and weak! Miserable creatures! There's no hope for you!

talk_anael_12903_2_4.kr: 인간의 마음은 우리와는 다르다. 언제 변할지 모르는 것. 어떻게 그들에게 미래를 맡길 수 있느냐!
talk_anael_12903_2_4.en: Humans...They are different from us. You never know when they'll change their mind! How can you put the fate of the future in such hands?

talk_anael_12903_2_5.kr: 헤븐즈 게이트가 너희를 경계할 것이다. 강승준!
talk_anael_12903_2_5.en: The Heaven's Gate will be watching you, Sam!

talk_anael_12903_3.kr: 잘도 여기까지 왔구나. 지구 인간들 주제에!
talk_anael_12903_3.en: Surprising that you've come this far, Human.

talk_anael_12903_4.kr: 하지만 갤럭시 리그에선 그만 꺼지거라. 우리 헤븐즈 게이트가 왔으니.
talk_anael_12903_4.en: But now it's time for you to leave the Galaxy League. You stand against the Heaven's Gate!

talk_anael_12903_6.kr: 나는 헤븐즈 게이트의 아나엘. 너희 세계에서 천사라 부르는 존재다.
talk_anael_12903_6.en: I am Anael, captain of the Heaven's Gate. You may know us as angels.

talk_anael_12903_7.kr: 갤럭시 리그가 뭔지도 모르고 참가한 어중이떠중이와 상대해야 하다니, 시간 낭비군.
talk_anael_12903_7.en: What a total waste of time to play against a group of amateurs who don't even know what the Galaxy League is.

talk_anael_12903_9.kr: 세레나. 너는 아직도 인간 따위에게 숨겨진 힘이 있다는 헛된 희망을 가지고 있는가?
talk_anael_12903_9.en: Selena...I see you still keep up that useless hope trying to find strength in Humanity.

talk_baltheon_13503_1.kr: 더 챔피온스가 올라왔다고? 헤븐즈게이트가 아니라니… 운이 좋았나 보군.
talk_baltheon_13503_1.en: We're up against the Champions? They must have gotten lucky against the Heaven's Gate.

talk_baltheon_13503_11.en: Silence! Witness the power of Cruzentes!

talk_baltheon_13503_2_4.kr: 반칙? 결국 골을 넣는 것이 승리 아닌가? 우린 룰을 지켰다.
talk_baltheon_13503_2_4.en: Foul? Winning is what the Galaxy League is all about! We played by the rules.

talk_baltheon_13503_2_5.kr: 하지만 지다니.. 믿을 수 없다. 너희에게 복수할 것이다!
talk_baltheon_13503_2_5.en: I can't believe we lost. You guys will pay for this!

talk_baltheon_13503_2_7.kr: 크루젠테스의 야망이 한 걸음 멀어진 대가를 치르게 해 주겠다.
talk_baltheon_13503_2_7.en: You must pay the price for standing against the entire Cruzentes!

talk_baltheon_13503_2_8.kr: 이제 헤븐즈 게이트가 아닌 너희 인간들이 우리의 적이 되었다.
talk_baltheon_13503_2_8.en: Forget about the Heaven's Gate. Now we consider you as our enemy!

talk_baltheon_13503_2_9.kr: 편한 리그가 되지 않으리라 맹세하지. 크흐흐흐!
talk_baltheon_13503_2_9.en: We assure you, this won't be an easy League for you guys. Haha!

talk_baltheon_13503_3.kr: 헤븐즈 게이트 놈들에 대한 이 원한을 풀 수 없다니!!
talk_baltheon_13503_3.en: I wanted to get back at those angels.

talk_baltheon_13503_4.kr: 강승준! 너는 내 복수의 기회를 빼앗았다!
talk_baltheon_13503_4.en: Well I guess I'll have to point this hatred towards you, Sam!

talk_baltheon_13503_5.kr: 저번 리그에서 이긴 걸 후회하게 해 주지.
talk_baltheon_13503_5.en: I'll make you regret coming up this far!

talk_baltheon_13503_9.kr: 나를 헬리온의 악마들 따위로 생각하는 거냐!
talk_baltheon_13503_9.en: How dare you compare me with the Demons of Hellion?

talk_brit_10.kr: 드리블로 돌파했으니 한 번 더 기회가 있어.
talk_brit_10.en: I penetrated their lines, so I get another chance!

talk_brit_11.en: We've got to steal the ball!

talk_brit_12.en: Don't tell me what to do!

talk_brit_19.en: We're about to find out about that!

talk_brit_2.en: Them! You won't get away with this!

talk_brit_21.en: I don't know if I could get past their lines even if I get the ball!

talk_brit_3.kr: 노아, 관둬. 내가 도전했고, 분하지만 졌어.
talk_brit_3.en: Noa, stop...I challenged them...and I lost...

talk_brit_4.en: Okay, we're starting off with the Woo Shin 2nd Stringers.

talk_brit_8.en: I'll pull it off this time!

talk_bythos_17103_1.kr: 크하하하핫! 어쩌다 상위 리그에 올라온 애송이를 짓밟아줄 기회가 왔군!
talk_bythos_17103_1.en: Haha! Look at what we've got here! Puney, weak, mortal beings!

talk_bythos_17103_2_1.en: No! This can't be possible! I..! I..!

talk_bythos_17103_4.kr: 봤느냐. 우리 헬리온과, 동맹 크루젠테스가 모든 리그를 지배하게 될 것이다.
talk_bythos_17103_4.en: The alliance of Hellion and Cruzentes will rule every League of the universe!

talk_bythos_17103_5.en: I, Vitos, will rule the universe!

talk_bythos_17103_8.en: Argh! Enough! Ready yourself for the ultimate punishment!

talk_cassiel_15903_11.kr: 끄응. 상대 팀 주장에게 부끄러운 모습을 보였군. 지금 시작하지!
talk_cassiel_15903_11.en: Sorry to keep you waiting. Let's begin.

talk_cassiel_15903_2_2.kr: 책을 본다고 결과가 달라지진 않았다. 마리엘, 인정할건 인정하자.
talk_cassiel_15903_2_2.en: That wouldn't have made much of a difference, Mariel.

talk_cassiel_15903_2_5.kr: 그래. 네가 정한 룰 안에서 경기에 임하면 그것으로 충분하다. 마리엘
talk_cassiel_15903_2_5.en: You don't have to, Mariel. Just follow your own rules. That's enough.

talk_cassiel_15903_8.kr:
그럴 때가 아니다. 마리엘
시합이 시작되고 있다는 걸 잊었나?
talk_cassiel_15903_8.en: Now's not the time for reading, Mariel. The game is about to start.

talk_cynthia_15302_2_3.kr: 이런 경기를 인정할 수 없어. 너희들 다 꺼져!
talk_cynthia_15302_2_3.en: This can't be! Get out of my sight!

talk_cynthia_15302_2_5.kr: 지다니?? 그, 그런 불쾌한 일 없었어!!
talk_cynthia_15302_2_5.en: Defeat...Never in my life has this occured!

talk_cynthia_15302_2_6.kr: 그나저나 너. 꽤 쓸만한 실력이 있어 보이는데. 이름이 뭐지?
talk_cynthia_15302_2_6.en: Oh, well. Anyways, you do show great potential. What's your name?

talk_cynthia_15302_4.kr: 무슨 소리! 갤럭시 리그를 만든 건 바로 우리. 미네르바 왕국이다.
talk_cynthia_15302_4.en: Are you out of your mind? How dare you see soccer as just a sport?

talk_cynthia_15302_5.kr: 축구를 공놀이 취급하다니! 정신 머리가 글렀군?

talk_cynthia_15302_6.en: Minerva Kingdom has made the Galaxy League. But we should've never allowed people like you to enter.

talk_eve_1.kr: 기회는 다시 오지 않아. 마지막으로 권유하건대, 계약해라.
talk_eve_1.en: This is my final offer. Sign the contract!

talk_eve_10.kr: 계약자로써 내게 명령해라 축구 경기를 허락해달라고.
talk_eve_10.en: If you want the Match, just say the words!

talk_eve_11.kr:
저들은 혼돈의 근원이다.
지구에서 축구를 좋아하는 모든 이들의 희망을 빼앗을 거야.
talk_eve_11.en:
They are the source of chaos. 
They're here to take away the hope of everybody on Earth who loves soccer.

talk_eve_12301_14.kr: 지금 너희 팀으로 앞으로의 리그가 어렵다는 건 너도 알 텐데?
talk_eve_12301_14.en: You should know that your team is not fit to climb up the ladder.

talk_eve_12301_15.en: You've lost a lot of players, right?

talk_eve_12301_20.kr: 그래도 세레나가 선택한 팀이라면, 승산이 있을 거야. 노아.
talk_eve_12301_20.en: But they are the ones selected by Selena. Hmm, what should we do.

talk_eve_12301_2_12.kr: 너의 강승준을 뺏어 가려는 게 아니다, 세레나. 난 평화로운 제안을 하고 있어.
talk_eve_12301_2_12.en: We're not here to take Sam away from you, Selena. I'm here to propose a treaty.

talk_eve_12301_2_2.en: You prove yourself worthy! Sign the contract!

talk_eve_12301_2_5.kr: 세레나, 네가 왜 안 나타나나 했어.
talk_eve_12301_2_5.en: Selena, I was wondering where you were.

talk_eve_12301_2_6.kr: 별로 달갑진 않지만, 우리 힘을 합쳐야 할 것 같다.
talk_eve_12301_2_6.en: I don't like it either, but I agree that we should combine strengths.

talk_eve_12301_4.kr: 노아, 정말 이런 녀석이랑 함께 해야 하는 거야?
talk_eve_12301_4.en: Noa. Do you really think we have to team up with these guys?

talk_eve_12301_7.kr: 그…그렇긴 하지만, 더 나은 팀이 있지 않을까?
talk_eve_12301_7.en: I...I know that but...Do you think we can find a better team?

talk_eve_13.en: Ami will be great help, but be careful.

talk_eve_14.kr: 저들이 이기기 위해 수단과 방법을 가리지 않을 거야.
talk_eve_14.en: They don't play fair and square. They'll do whatever it takes to win.

talk_eve_15.en: Ami, aren't you like 1700 years old?

talk_eve_17.kr:
이걸로 당분간 저 놈들이 
지구에 매치를 걸 순 없을 거다.
talk_eve_17.en:
That ought to keep them 
from challenging Earth for a while.

talk_eve_19.kr: 저들은 피스메이커. 시공의 혼돈을 불러일으키는 자들.
talk_eve_19.en: They're Peacemakers. They are the ones causing chaos throughout time and space.

talk_eve_2.kr: 우주의 혼돈을 바로잡을 수 있는 좋은 기회인데 뭘 망설이지? 고민하지마.
talk_eve_2.en: This is an opportunity of a lifetime! To set order in the Universe and fight against chaos! Why not?

talk_eve_20.en: They are the ones we must stop.

talk_eve_21.kr: 이 우주에는 암묵적으로 지켜져 온 거대한 규칙이 있다.
talk_eve_21.en: The universe is ruled by one secret rule.

talk_eve_22.en: It's a soccer league called the Galaxy League.

talk_eve_23.kr: 전쟁과 무력충돌을 막기 위한 수단이라고 말하지만 하지만,
talk_eve_23.en: It's the sole way to solve conflict in the universe, invented to prevent war and physical conflict.

talk_eve_24.kr:
거기서 승리한 자만이 모든걸 얻는다.
그것은 결국 또 다른 전쟁이지.
talk_eve_24.en:
But this is a game where winner takes all. 
It's a war with another face.

talk_eve_25.kr: 이미 우리 별의 종족들도 그 권력을 얻기 위해 움직이기 시작했다.
talk_eve_25.en: Our race has been busy moving around to secure good seats in this war.

talk_eve_26.kr: 하지만 난 보이지 않는 곳에서 움직이는 거대한 음모를 눈치챘지
talk_eve_26.en: But I found out something. A deeper conspiracy.

talk_eve_27.en: I'm a prophet. I thought you'd be the one.

talk_eve_28.kr: 이 거대한 혼돈에서 흔들리지 않을 단 하나의 영웅.
talk_eve_28.en: The one that will save the universe from falling in the hands of chaos.

talk_eve_29.kr: 나와 계약하자. 너의 축구로 혼돈을 파괴하는 거다.
talk_eve_29.en: Sign a contract with me. Together we could win against chaos.

talk_eve_3.kr: 악마에게 대항하는 그 기세를 높이 사, 계약을 허락해주마
talk_eve_3.en: I like your attitude. Good! I allow you to sign the contract!

talk_eve_30.kr: 계약과 동시에 넌 내 마스터가 된다.
talk_eve_30.en: Sign this contract and you become my Master.

talk_eve_31.kr: 부담 가질 건 없어. 날 따라 하면 돼.
talk_eve_31.en: Nothing to feel pressure about. Repeat after me.

talk_eve_32.en: I seal the pact of blood.

talk_eve_35.kr:
계약 해 봤자 난 별다른 힘도 없고
이대로도 좋다고 생각한 거야.
talk_eve_35.en:
I just thought you'd be fine all by yourself. 
It's not like I could grant you any super powers or something.

talk_eve_36.en: Wow. You should stop reading science fiction, girl.

talk_eve_38.kr:
난 두 번은 설명 안해.
한 눈 팔지 말고 한 번에 잘 들어.
talk_eve_38.en:
Anyways, I've heard that the High School Leagues aren't far away. 
This would be a good experience for you.

talk_eve_39.en: Let's get you a team first.

talk_eve_4.kr: 신에게 굴복하지 않다니, 근성이 뛰어난 인간이로군.
talk_eve_4.en: You are one strong human, not bowing down to superior power!

talk_eve_41.kr: 좋아. 여기서 편성을 선택하면 편성이 가능해져.

talk_eve_42.kr:
편성 화면이군.
이제 화살표로 표시한 선수를 터치해
talk_eve_42.en:
This is where you put the Players where you want them to be 
and build up the team Formation.

talk_eve_43.kr: 선택한 선수는 축구 포지션이면 어디든지 자유롭게 배치 가능하다구.
talk_eve_43.en: Players can be placed wherever you want them to be.

talk_eve_44.en: Tap Auto Place to automatically set up the Formation.

talk_eve_45.kr: 정보보기를 통해 주력 포지션을 확인하거나 스킬도 볼 수 있다는 것 잊지마.
talk_eve_45.en: Don't forget that you can see the Skills and preferred Positions of the Players when you tap View Info.

talk_eve_46.kr: COST를 넘겨서 선수를 배치할 수 없다는 것 정도는 알고 있겠지?
talk_eve_46.en: Oh yeah, and you can't go over the Max. Cost when you're placing Players.

talk_eve_47.kr:
지금 당장은 화살표가 가리키는 곳에
선수를 이동시켜봐
talk_eve_47.en:
For now try placing a Player 
 where the arrow is pointing to.

talk_eve_48.kr: 나쁘지 않아. 그럼 실전 연습을 해볼까?
talk_eve_48.en: Not bad! Now let's go on with a real match.

talk_eve_49.kr: 스토리모드로 들어가면 기본적인 경기가 엄청나게 많아.
talk_eve_49.en: Go to the Story Mode. There's a lot of Matches ready for you there.

talk_eve_5.kr: 이제 거의 마음을 돌린 것 같으니 이제 내일 다시 오자꾸나.
talk_eve_5.en: I'm sure you'll reconsider. I hope to hear some good news next time!

talk_eve_51.kr:
친구가 되면, 친구의 에이스 선수를 이용해 
경기를 쉽게 풀어갈 수도 있다구.
talk_eve_51.en: If you become Friends with another User, you can use your Friend's Ace Player to make the Match easier.

talk_eve_52.en: Follow me. Let me show you how to Train your Players.

talk_eve_53.en: The Train button is also at the Player Menu.

talk_eve_55.en: Now choose which Player you'd like to Train.

talk_eve_57.kr: 이번에는 재료 선수야. 재료는 훈련 후 사라지니까 주의하라구.
talk_eve_57.en: Now it's time for you to pick the Player you'd like to use as material. Remember that they disappear after Training.

talk_eve_59.kr: 훈련하면 경험치가 오르고 선수의 능력치가 증가한다.
talk_eve_59.en: If you Train, the Player's EXP and stats increase.

talk_eve_60.en: Let's call it a day for Training.

talk_eve_62.kr: 우리 팀 매니저를 소개하지. 숙소의 집사도 겸할 예정이야.
talk_eve_62.en: I'd like to introduce you to the team Manager. He'll also be the house keeper.

talk_eve_63.kr: 매니저 스킬 사용에는 각자 일정 시간이 필요해.
talk_eve_63.en: Manager Skills need some time to be prepared.

talk_eve_64.kr: 매니저 종류마다 배치할 수 있는 위치가 다르다는 점도 기억하라구.
talk_eve_64.en: Don't forget that you can place Managers in different positions according to their type.

talk_eve_65.kr: 대단해. 진짜로 할 수 있을지도 모르겠는걸?
talk_eve_65.en: Wow, I knew you had talent but that was impressive!

talk_eve_66.en: I see you're ready. Let me tell you about Free Matches.

talk_eve_68.kr: 한 번 클리어한 리그는 다시 도전할 수가 있는데 여기에 보너스 미션으로 보상이 있어.
talk_eve_68.en: You can re-play the Leagues you've already won. When you re-play, you'll be provided with Bonus Missions that come with various Rewards!

talk_eve_69.kr: 뭐, 선택적인 부분이라 내키지 않으면 리그매치만 진행해도 좋아.
talk_eve_69.en: Well, this is optional, so you could just focus on League Matches if you want.

talk_eve_70.kr: 그럼 이쯤에서 마지막으로 선수 뽑기를 해볼까?
talk_eve_70.en: Now, for the final lesson. Let's try out Drawing Players.

talk_eve_72.kr: 여기가 뽑기 화면, 유료로 레어 선수 뽑기와 일반 선수 뽑기가 있다.
talk_eve_72.en: This is the Draw Menu. You can either Draw Rare Players with Crystals or go for the Normal Draw.

talk_eve_73.kr: 우선은 내가 가진 시공석으로 선수를 한 명 찾아 보도록 하겠다.
talk_eve_73.en: For this time only, I'll use the Crystals I have to find you a Player.

talk_eve_74.kr: 이건 '시공석'이다. 게임플레이를 통해 얻을 수도 있고 상점에서도 판매하고 있지.
talk_eve_74.en: It's what we call Crystals. You can earn them by playing the game or buy them at the Shop.

talk_eve_76.en: Hmm...Looks like we got a good Player.

talk_eve_77.kr:
그럼 지금까지 배운 것을 잘 기억하고, 
팀을 성장시켜 리그에 참가해보아라.
talk_eve_77.en:
Remember what you've learned today. 
Strengthen your team and enter the Galaxy League!

talk_eve_9.kr: 저것이 바로 내가 말한 혼돈이다. 축구로 이겨야만 해.
talk_eve_9.en: That is the chaos I've been talking about. Soccer is the only way to defeat them.

talk_gunsung_1_1.kr: 신화여고는 올해 축구팀이 창설돼서 전력은 알 수 없다. 우선 적 팀의 선공이니 주의토록.
talk_gunsung_1_1.en: There's not a lot of information on the Legend Women's High School's soccer team, because they're new. But be careful, since they'll be attacking first.

talk_gunsung_3.kr: 사정은 이미 들었다. 우선 잠시 따라와 봐.
talk_gunsung_3.en: I've heard the story. Follow me.

talk_gunsung_4.kr: 여기가 최강의 축구팀을 만들 본부다. 매니저들을 등록하는 곳이지.
talk_gunsung_4.en: This is our Team headquarters. This is where you register Managers.

talk_gunsung_5.kr: 자, 우선 날 매니저로 등록해 보라구.
talk_gunsung_5.en: Sign me up as a Manager.

talk_gunsung_6.kr:
좋다. 이걸로 내 능력 '근성'이 발동된다.
내가 있는 한 모든 선수의 피지컬이 증가할거다.
talk_gunsung_6.en:
Now my Manager Skill, Spirit, is in effect 
and will increase the Physical Stats of every Player.

talk_gunsung_7.kr: 추가로 강력한 액션도 취할 수 있지만 당장은 어렵겠어.
talk_gunsung_7.en: I have another powerful Skill you could use, but that's not available for now.

talk_leiden_10502_3.kr: 갤럭시 리그에 참가하겠다고 설치는 저급한 종족이 있다더니, 네놈들인가?
talk_leiden_10502_3.en: I've heard about this inferior race trying to play soccer at the Galaxy League. I assume its you.

talk_leiden_10502_4.kr: 황당하군, 레미. 네가 이런 허접한 놈들한테 지다니.
talk_leiden_10502_4.en: Ha! Lemi, I'm so disappointed that you've lost to these...Humans.

talk_leiden_10502_6.en: Silence! Your reputation proves to be too much for you!

talk_leiden_10502_7.kr: 타고난 신체를 그대로 사용하는 미개한 종족 따위, 부서 주마!
talk_leiden_10502_7.en: How could you lose to a savage race that uses its natural form to play soccer?!

talk_leiden_10502_9.kr: 사실을 말했을 뿐이다. 한 수 가르쳐주지.
talk_leiden_10502_9.en: I've said what is true, Human...Let me show you what real soccer is like.

talk_mariel_15903_1.kr: 당신이 다음 상대인가요? 천상의 축구를 보여주겠어요.
talk_mariel_15903_1.en: Are you our next opponent? We'll show you how soccer is played in heaven!

talk_mariel_15903_2_1.kr: 역시 저 책을 보고 나서 경기를 해야 했어요.
talk_mariel_15903_2_1.en: I should've read the book before the match!

talk_mariel_15903_2_3.kr:
헤븐즈 게이트의 명예가 실추되다니, 속상해요.
하지만 이 책은…. 안보길 잘했군요. 이렇게나 난폭하다니.
talk_mariel_15903_2_3.en: Heaven's Gate has lost...What a disgrace. But I feel comfortable now, Cassiel.

talk_mariel_15903_2_4.kr: 비록 우리가 지긴 했지만, 누군가를 다치게 하는 것은 싫어요. 오라버니.
talk_mariel_15903_2_4.en: I don't want to hurt anybody.

talk_mariel_15903_5.kr: 룰을 벗어난 공격은 안돼요. 적이 다칠 수도 있잖아요, 세이리우스!
talk_mariel_15903_5.en: Don't cheat! They could get hurt!

talk_mariel_15903_7.kr: 제가 안본 책이 있다니. 놀랍군요. 지금 당장 독파하겠습니다!
talk_mariel_15903_7.en: I've never read that book. Give it to me right now!

talk_mariel_15903_9.kr: 앗! 카시엘 오라버니. 왜 저 마도서는 제게 가르쳐 주시지 않은 거죠?
talk_mariel_15903_9.en: Cassiel! Why didn't you tell me about the book?

talk_narae_12301_18.kr: 노아, 우리가 이런 사람들이랑 같이 뛰어야 하는 거예요?
talk_narae_12301_18.en: Noa, I think we should reconsider playing with these guys.

talk_narae_12301_22.en: Beat us, and we'll become part of your team!

talk_noa_11.kr: 저놈들 아무리 봐도 나쁜 놈들 같긴 하지만…
talk_noa_11.en: They do look like the bad guys....

talk_noa_12.kr:
나도 싸우고싶다구!
하지만 지금 경기를 하려면 사람이 부족해.
talk_noa_12.en:
I want to fight! 
But we don't even have enough people to put up a Match!

talk_noa_12301_12.en: But I'm trying to group up with you.

talk_noa_12301_21.kr: 그건 두고 보면 알겠지. 이제 시합이니까.
talk_noa_12301_21.en: Let's watch how they play, and then decide.

talk_noa_12301_2_11.en: We found you on the entry list. That's all.

talk_noa_12301_2_14.kr: 그렇게 강요해서 될 일은 아니야. 아미.
talk_noa_12301_2_14.en: Now, now, Ami. We can't rush him like that.

talk_noa_12301_2_15.kr: 하지만 앞으로의 리그를 위해서 팀을 합치고 싶어. 강승준
talk_noa_12301_2_15.en: But I would like our teams to become one, for the sake of upcoming games.

talk_noa_12301_2_16.kr: 너희 팀도 힘들어 하고 있다고 들었으니까.
talk_noa_12301_2_16.en: I heard that your team is also having a hard time.

talk_noa_12301_6.en: You're the one who came up with the idea.

talk_noa_12301_8.en: There weren't any better teams, right?

talk_noa_13.kr: 좋아, 잘 할거라는 기대는 안 해, 방해만 말라구!
talk_noa_13.en: I don't expect much from you. Just stay out of my way.

talk_noa_13503_10.en: You do look like one of them.

talk_noa_13503_6.kr: 승준. 저 악마가 원맨쇼를 하는 것 같아.

talk_noa_13503_8.en: Yeah, he reminds me of Eve.

talk_noa_17.en: Uh, a little heads up with that kind of stuff would be nice.

talk_noa_17103_2_3.en: Wasn't he your former boss or something?

talk_noa_17103_7.en: Yeah...His name does sound like that snack we had back on Earth.

talk_noa_17503_2_4.kr: 그런데 저 소녀. 다가오는데? 인상이 좀… 달라졌어.
talk_noa_17503_2_4.en: The girl is coming towards us. She...Looks different.

talk_noa_2.kr: 고민한적 없어! 그리고 그 마지막 권유가 벌써 10번은 넘은 거 같은데!
talk_noa_2.en: I don't want to! And that was like the 10th final offer!

talk_noa_20.en: I don't like this one bit.

talk_noa_23.en: I mean, before that, who are you guys?

talk_noa_24.kr:
말이 안 되잖아. 시공이니 뭐니… 
조금이라도 상식적인 말을 하라구
talk_noa_24.en:
Uh, guys? Time and space? Chaos? 
This is a joke right?

talk_noa_26.kr:
좋아, 우주의 축구전쟁이라고 쳐.
난 왜 너랑 계약해야 되지?
talk_noa_26.en:
Okay, say this soccer space war is true. 
Why do I have to sign a contract with you?

talk_noa_30.kr: 축구에 지고 말도 안 되는 빛과 함께 사라진 놈들…
talk_noa_30.en: All that back there and this...

talk_noa_31.kr: 네 예언. 다 좋아, 맞다고 하자구.
talk_noa_31.en: Okay, okay. I'll believe you about the space and chaos story.

talk_noa_32.en: But I'm doing this with my own strength.

talk_noa_33.kr: 그게 사실이라면 내 힘으로. 축구로 이길 거라구.
talk_noa_33.en: I'm going to take matters into my own hands.

talk_noa_34.en: Uh, what? No begging me to reconsider?

talk_noa_35.kr: 에에??? 너 엄청난 힘이라도 있던 거 아니었어?
talk_noa_35.en: What? I thought you were some supernatural being!

talk_noa_37.en: Let's pass the ball around to look for chances!

talk_noa_39.kr: 이제 좀 강해진 거 같으니 다음 경기를 진행해볼까?
talk_noa_39.en: Now that you've gained some strength, how about another Match?

talk_noa_46.en: I think I know who you're talking about...

talk_noa_48.en: That's the front runner of this League!

talk_noa_49.en: Looks like this is going to be a tough game!

talk_noa_49_1.kr: 좋아 브릿트! 부탁할게. 너의 실력을 보여줘!
talk_noa_49_1.en: Great! I have faith in you!

talk_noa_5.en: We're just high school students! What are adults doing in this field?

talk_noa_50.en: Nice! I'll make this one count!

talk_noa_52.en: So this thing just keeps on going...

talk_noa_6.kr:
어떻게 나를 알고 있지?
당신들 대체 누구야?!
talk_noa_6.en:
Do you know me? 
How? Who are you people?

talk_noa_7.en: I guess today's my lucky day!

talk_noa_9.en: I have no idea what you guys are talking about!

talk_phoenix_14702_11.kr: 네가 미래의 영웅을 보호하고 있다는 소문은, 익히 들었어.
talk_phoenix_14702_11.en: I heard that you're trying to protect that so called future hero.

talk_phoenix_14702_12.kr: 하지만 저 인간 따위를 영웅으로 만들려는 거야?
talk_phoenix_14702_12.en: But why are you trying to make a hero out of a Human?

talk_phoenix_14702_14.kr: 그렇다. 난 세레나의 선택을 믿지만 그녀가 날 선택했음 좋겠군.
talk_phoenix_14702_14.en: I believe you Selena. But I wish you'd choose me.

talk_phoenix_14702_15.kr: 세레나는 이 우주에 몇 안되는 예언자니까 말야.
talk_phoenix_14702_15.en: Selena is one of the few prophets in the universe.

talk_phoenix_14702_17.kr: 그런 말을 듣기 위해 온 게 아니다.
talk_phoenix_14702_17.en: I'm not here for your apologies.

talk_phoenix_14702_18.en: Sam. Give up Selena if you lose.

talk_phoenix_14702_2_2.kr: 넌 고작. 아직 어린 인간일 뿐인데!
talk_phoenix_14702_2_2.en: You..You are only just a Human! A young one too!

talk_phoenix_14702_2_5.kr: 난… 아직 인정할 수 없다. 설령 미네르바 왕국의 왕녀가 인정한다 해도. 우리 카르티나는!
talk_phoenix_14702_2_5.en: I can't admit this! Even if the Queen of Minerva Kingdom approves this, Katrina Association is against this decision!

talk_phoenix_14702_7.kr: 확인하고 싶은 게 있을 뿐이야. 강승준.
talk_phoenix_14702_7.en: I just came to check something, Sam.

talk_phoenix_14702_8.kr: 그리고… 말을 잘 알아듣지 못하는군, 세레나.
talk_phoenix_14702_8.en: And, I wasn't looking for him, Selena.

talk_phoenix_14702_9.kr: 난 강승준이 아니라 널 찾았을 뿐이야.

talk_ray_1.en:
You're Sam? 
Is this some kind of joke?

talk_ray_10.kr:
알 거 없어. 열 받으면, 
붙어볼래?
talk_ray_10.en:
None of your business! 
If you want answers, fight for it!

talk_ray_11.kr: 축. 구. 로. 말. 이. 야!

talk_ray_13.kr: 잠… 깐만 내 이야기 안 끝났는데
talk_ray_13.en: Uh, I'm not done talking yet...

talk_ray_14.en: Doesn't matter. We'll squash them all!

talk_ray_2.kr:
쪼그만게 완전히 약하게 생겼잖아. 
영웅이라고 해봐야 아무도 안 믿겠군. 하하하.
talk_ray_2.en:
This puny little fellow is going to become the intergalactic soccer fantasy star? 
Ha! What a disappointment!

talk_ray_3.en:
None of your business! 
If you want answers, fight for it!

talk_ray_4.kr: 축. 구. 로. 말. 이. 야!

talk_ray_5.en: Doesn't matter. We'll squash them all!

talk_ray_6.kr:
햇병아리 같은 실력으론 
리그에 참가조차 할 수 없다는 걸 알려주마!
talk_ray_6.en:
Let's show them what it takes 
to be in the League!

talk_ray_8.kr:
기세만 살았군 흐흐흐.
이게 지구 축구의 수준인 거냐?
talk_ray_8.en:
I see you're good at one thing. Talking! 
Is this all Earth has got for soccer? Such a disappointment...

talk_reanbell_17503_1.kr: 모든 것은 그분의 뜻! 나는 질 수 없어요!
talk_reanbell_17503_1.en: Following the will of the almighty, I am not to lose!

talk_reanbell_17503_2.kr: 오빠, 오빠도 도와줄 거지? 내 힘이 되어 줄거지?

talk_reanbell_17503_2_11.kr: 이젠 돌이킬 수 없게 되었어요. 베라모드의 계획대로.
talk_reanbell_17503_2_11.en: Everything will be as Veramod plans.

talk_reanbell_17503_2_12.en: Now the wheels of fortune are set in motion. It can't be stopped.

talk_reanbell_17503_2_8.kr: 이기고 싶었어요. 내 머릿속에 온통 지라는 말 뿐이었는데도.
talk_reanbell_17503_2_8.en: I wanted to win. Even though the voice was telling me to lose.

talk_reanbell_17503_2_9.kr: 내 본능 어딘가가 이겨야 한다고… 그래서 최선을 다했는데. 흑…
talk_reanbell_17503_2_9.en: But I wanted to win. So I tried very hard. But...But...

talk_reanbell_17503_3.kr: 응 린벨. 내가 네 곁에 있을게.

talk_reanbell_17503_7.kr: 승준.. 강승준!? 모든것의 시작은 당신이었어요! 쓰러뜨리겠어요!
talk_reanbell_17503_7.en: Sam? So you are where it all begins! I must take you down!

talk_retre_10203_11.en: Humans...Haven't you heard about dimension traveling?

talk_retre_10203_13.en: My name is Retre. I'm a Gate Keeper.

talk_retre_10203_15.kr: 움브라 행성의 축제리그에 갈 거라고 했지?
talk_retre_10203_15.en: You asked for a ride to the Planet Umbra, right?

talk_retre_10301_3.kr: 고럼. 눈 깜짝할 시간이면 옮겨줄 수 있지. 에헴!
talk_retre_10301_3.en: Yes. We traveled through dimensions and have arrived at the Planet Umbra.

talk_robin_16502_1.kr: 으흐흐흐흐. 날 출전시키겠다고? 각오는 했겠지. 큭큭..
talk_robin_16502_1.en: Are you really sure you want me on the field? Hehehehe!

talk_robin_16502_13.en: Kick off! I'm going to enjoy this!

talk_robin_16502_2_1.en: Oooh! I hate these hand cuffs!

talk_robin_16502_2_7.en: Did you just address me as a Villain? Splendid!

talk_robin_16502_2_8.kr: 마음에 드는 호칭이군. 찾을 테다. 그들을 찾아….!
talk_robin_16502_2_8.en: I like the ring to that word...Villain...Hehe!

talk_robin_16502_3.en: Why would I? I'm about to have so much fun!

talk_robin_16502_8.en: Whee! I'm going to have so much fun beating you down!

talk_ryle_10502_1.kr: 이 행성 사람들은 다들 늘씬하고, 운동신경이 장난이 아닌걸?
talk_ryle_10502_1.en: The Players from this planet are so fast and strong!

talk_ryle_11.kr: 돌파하여 라인을 전진했으니 나에게 한번 더 공격 기회가 있어!
talk_ryle_11.en: So I get another chance to press forward whenever I manage to Penetrate? Nice!

talk_ryle_11703_5.en: Look at their entry list. Look at their ace...

talk_ryle_12.en: I've got to steal the ball from him!

talk_ryle_13.en: Got it! Let's go for it!

talk_ryle_14.en: Yeah! That's right! That's what you get for going up against me!

talk_ryle_19.en: We're up against the front runner of this League!

talk_ryle_2.kr:
승준아, 저 녀석들! 무작정 도전해왔어… 
자존심에 상대는 해 줬지만…
talk_ryle_2.en:
Sam, it's them! They just came and challenged us...
We accepted it...but...

talk_ryle_22.kr: 공을 다시 넘겨 받더라도 MF 라인을 뚫을 수 있을지 모르겠어!
talk_ryle_22.en: I don't know if I can penetrate their MF lines even if I get the ball back!

talk_ryle_23.en: I can't believe it! Did we actually win the League?

talk_ryle_3.en:
Don't do it Sam! 
They're too powerful...!

talk_ryle_5.en: Look. It's the 2nd Stringers for Woo Shin. This should be easy.

talk_ryle_6.en: Time to show off my moves!

talk_ryle_8.en: Did I get too ahead of myself?

talk_ryle_9.kr: 음…패스를 받으면 강해지니까 이번에는 꼭 해내겠어!
talk_ryle_9.en: Receiving the Pass will grant me extra Attacking Power. I'll be able to make it this time!

talk_seirius_15903_3.kr: 그럼요. 히힛! 아브라카타브라!!! 하면 여기 선수가 저기서 뿅!
talk_seirius_15903_3.en: See for yourself! Abracadabra! Come, my Players!

talk_seirius_15903_4.kr: 그러다 보면 우리가 이길 거예요. 히히히힛!

talk_seirius_15903_6.kr: 흐응- 갤럭시 리그에서는 자신의 능력을 최대한 활용해도 된다고 이렇게 제 마도서에 적혀 있다구욧!
talk_seirius_15903_6.en: It says in the book that you can do whatever you're capable of!

talk_serena_1.kr:
승준님! 드디어 발견했군요! 
제 이야기 좀 들어주시겠어요?
talk_serena_1.en:
Sam! I finally found you! 
Could you hear me out for a moment?

talk_serena_10.kr:
저들은 미래의 지구 대표를 이끌 
승준님을 찾아 온 거예요.
talk_serena_10.en:
They're here for you Sam! 
The future captain of Team Earth!

talk_serena_10203_3.kr: 네! 이제 지구를 위해, 승준님이 갤럭시 리그에 참가할 수 있게 되었어요.
talk_serena_10203_3.en: Not quite. Now you've just earned the right to enter the Galaxy League.

talk_serena_10203_5.kr: 으응? 끝이라뇨. 저 우주에 얼마나 많은 리그들이 있는데요!
talk_serena_10203_5.en: The universe is vast and there are numerous Leagues. Of course it isn't the end!

talk_serena_10203_8.kr: 뭐, 4족보행 행성도 있긴 하지만, 갤럭시 리그의 룰은 전 우주가 동일해요.
talk_serena_10203_8.en: Of course! There are some aliens with 4 legs and stuff, but they all play by the same rule.

talk_serena_10301_2_2.kr: 이렇게 다른 은하와 승부하며 계속 실력을 기르면… 언젠가 그들을 만날 수 있어요.
talk_serena_10301_2_2.en: Keep winning like this and someday you may meet...Them.

talk_serena_10301_2_5.en: Later! We've got a new match ready!

talk_serena_10301_2_6.en: I'll be aiding you all the way!

talk_serena_10301_5.en: Retre will take care of that!

talk_serena_10301_6.kr: 그것보다, 벌써 경기가 시작되려나 봐요. 우리도 어서 참가하죠!
talk_serena_10301_6.en: Oh, the games are about to start! Let's go! Hurry!

talk_serena_10502_2_2.kr: 메트로시티는 멸망을 경험하고 새롭게 태어난 강화 인류. 그런 자들을 이기다니 정말 대단해요!
talk_serena_10502_2_2.en: Metrocity is a race of artificially enhanced Humans that have been revived from near extinction. You've taught them a lesson!

talk_serena_11.kr:
저희가 이길 수 있다면, 저들을 지구에서 
더 이상 날뛰지 못하게 할 수 있어요.
talk_serena_11.en:
If we defeat them, they won't 
be able to terrorize Earth anymore!

talk_serena_11101_1.en: We made it to the Galaxy League!

talk_serena_11101_11.en: You could say that, but technically it's not.

talk_serena_11101_12.kr: 한번 우승한다고 해도, 영원히 계속 우승할 수는 없으니까요.
talk_serena_11101_12.en: It's impossible to become the everlasting champion in the Galaxy League.

talk_serena_11101_13.kr: 전 은하의 축구 팀들은 자신들의 룰을 이루기 위해 도전해올 거예요.
talk_serena_11101_13.en: Every soccer team in the galaxy will try out for the Galaxy League and aim for the championship.

talk_serena_11101_14.en: You, Sam, just became one of the challengers.

talk_serena_11101_16.kr: 어머, 제가 전에 말씀 안 드렸었나요?
talk_serena_11101_16.en: Didn't I tell you about this before?

talk_serena_11101_19.kr: 앗! 경기가 시작되려나 봐요. 승준님! 힘내서 이기셔야 해요!!
talk_serena_11101_19.en: Oh, look! Your next match is about to start! Go get 'em!

talk_serena_11101_3.kr: 네, 첫 출전이라 비록 하부리그이지만 계속 승리하면 상부 리그로 올라갈 수 있어요.
talk_serena_11101_3.en: Yes! We're the new team here so we've got to start from the bottom, but I'm sure we can make it to the top!

talk_serena_11101_5.kr: 리그는 전 은하계의 룰이에요. 즉… 은하의 규칙을 만들 수도 없앨 수도 있죠.
talk_serena_11101_5.en: The winner gets to change the rules of the universe. They can also make or eliminate rules as well.

talk_serena_11101_7.kr: 네. 한 종족의 수명이나 문화, 관습 같은 모든 것을 결정할 수 있어요.
talk_serena_11101_7.en: Yes. Through rules, they can even decide the fate of an entire race.

talk_serena_11101_8.kr: 갤럭시 리그에서 우승하면, 원하는 것 한가지를 결정할 수 있는 권한을 얻죠.
talk_serena_11101_8.en: The winner of the Galaxy League gets to change one rule. One of the rules of the universe.

talk_serena_11101_9.kr: 바꿀 수 없는 것은 갤럭시 리그 승부의 룰 하나뿐이에요.
talk_serena_11101_9.en: The only thing that can't be touched are the rules regarding the Galaxy League itself.

talk_serena_11103_2_5.en: They're the reason why the Galaxy League was born!

talk_serena_11103_2_6.kr: 그만큼 난폭하고 또 강력한 실력을 가지고 있어요.

talk_serena_11103_2_8.en: That's the spirit! Go for it, Sam!

talk_serena_12.en: We lose our right to play in the League for a while.

talk_serena_12903_2_10.kr: 하지만 승준님은 그렇지 않을 거라는걸 전 봤어요.
talk_serena_12903_2_10.en: But from what I've seen of you, there's nothing to worry about.

talk_serena_12903_2_12.en: I can't tell you about that...For now...

talk_serena_12903_2_13.kr: 하지만 승준님은 항상 바른 선택을 하실 거에요. 전 그런 승준님을 믿어요.
talk_serena_12903_2_13.en: But I can tell you this. You've always made the right decision. I have trust in you.

talk_serena_12903_2_2.kr: 아나엘님. 이 분이 제가 찾은 해답이에요. 아시겠나요?
talk_serena_12903_2_2.en: Anael. This is the one I've been looking for. Can you see why?

talk_serena_12903_2_8.kr: 그들은 승준님의 힘을 두려워하는 것 뿐이에요.
talk_serena_12903_2_8.en: They're just afraid of your potential, Sam.

talk_serena_12903_2_9.kr: 힘있는 자들은 악한 마음을 가지기도 쉬운 법이니까요.
talk_serena_12903_2_9.en: Ones with power always have the possibility to make the wrong decisions...

talk_serena_12903_8.kr: 저희도 참가 자격이 있어요! 깔보지 마세요.
talk_serena_12903_8.en: We are qualified to join the League! Take that back!

talk_serena_13.en: The League is the fate of the Galaxy and the only rule that exists.

talk_serena_14.kr:
저들은 지금 미래 경쟁자들의 희망을 빼앗아, 
우주의 운명을 가지고 놀려 한다구요!
talk_serena_14.en:
They're trying to eliminate the competition by jumping to the past! 
They're trying to manipulate the fate and order of the Galaxy!

talk_serena_14702_1.en: There's someone who'd like to meet you.

talk_serena_14702_16.kr: 전 주작님은 응원할 수 없어요. 죄송해요.
talk_serena_14702_16.en: I can't support you, Vermilion Bird. I'm sorry.

talk_serena_14702_2_10.kr: 처음 만났을 때 말씀 드렸듯이, 전 미래의 영웅을 지키기 위해 왔어요.
talk_serena_14702_2_10.en: Like I said from the very beginning, my sole purpose is to protect the hero of the future.

talk_serena_14702_2_12.kr: 예언이라는 건 미래로 향하는 길. 우리 예언자의 의지는 미래에 영향을 끼쳐요.
talk_serena_14702_2_12.en: A prophecy is the path to the future. The will of us prophets have an impact on the future.

talk_serena_14702_2_14.kr: 그렇진 않아요. 승준님. 상대방 팀에 영향은 끼칠 수도 있지만…
talk_serena_14702_2_14.en: No, Sam. It's not that. I could influence the other team...

talk_serena_14702_2_15.kr: 예언자가 바라는 순간 그 예언은 힘을 잃어요.
talk_serena_14702_2_15.en: But as soon as a prophet starts to wish for something, the prophecy loses its power.

talk_serena_14702_2_16.kr: 그렇기에 제 예언은 미래로 향하는 길이자, 미래를 방해하는 길.
talk_serena_14702_2_16.en: The prophecies I speak of are the paths to the future, but at the same time are also the paths that disturb the future.

talk_serena_14702_2_17.kr: 이 길을 찾는 건 승준님의 역할이에요.
talk_serena_14702_2_17.en: The one to find the right path is you, Sam.

talk_serena_14702_2_4.en: And my decision remains the same.

talk_serena_14702_2_8.kr: 전 미네르바의 왕녀는 아니에요. 그분 역시 승준님께 관심이 있다고는 들었지만요.
talk_serena_14702_2_8.en: I'm not the Queen if that's what you're asking. But I heard that she too has interest in you, Sam.

talk_serena_14702_3.en: It's Vermilion Bird. You're playing against his team this time.

talk_serena_15.kr:
도전을 받아들이세요! 여기서 거부한다면, 
더 많은 지구의 축구선수들이 절망에 빠질꺼에요.
talk_serena_15.en:
Accept the challenge! They won't stop here even if you don't! 
More future Soccer heroes will be in despair!

talk_serena_15302_2.kr: 여긴 최후의 전쟁 전에 은하를 지배하던 성소예요.
talk_serena_15302_2.en: This is the Temple that ruled the universe before the Final War.

talk_serena_15903_2_7.kr: 헤븐즈 게이트의 천사들은 가끔 너무 착해서 경기에 패배할 때도 있어요.
talk_serena_15903_2_7.en: Angels often lose the game because they're too kind.

talk_serena_15903_2_8.kr: 하지만 모두가 착하기만 하진 않죠. 그들도 평화를 쟁취하길 원하니까요.
talk_serena_15903_2_8.en: But not all Angels are like them. So be careful.

talk_serena_16502_2_5.kr: 승준님 참으세요. 저들에겐 선과 악의 개념 따위 없어요.
talk_serena_16502_2_5.en: Sam! Back off! They don't know the line that divides good from evil!

talk_serena_16502_2_6.kr: 입력된 룰대로 움직이는 자들이잖아요. 어쩌다 저런 변형개체가 나왔는지는 모르지만…
talk_serena_16502_2_6.en: They're just moving by inputted codes! I don't know how they came up with something like that, but you can't express your anger like this!

talk_serena_16502_2_9.en: Let's go. I'm getting the creeps.

talk_serena_16502_4.kr: 적팀 출전자가.. 너무 위험해 보여요. 괜찮을까요?
talk_serena_16502_4.en: There seems to be something wrong with that Player. Be careful!

talk_serena_16502_5.kr: 이상하네요. 메트로시티에 저런 선수가 있다니, 들어보지 못했다구요!
talk_serena_16502_5.en: I've never heard of that Player playing for Metrocity.

talk_serena_17.kr:
큐레스씨는 저런 피스메이커들을 막는 임무를 가졌어요. 
함께 싸우면 큰 도움이 될 거에요!
talk_serena_17.en:
It's Mr. Cules's job to stop those Peacemakers. 
You'll find that Mr. Cule is very good at his job.

talk_serena_17503_5.kr: 저 소녀 안에 죽음이 있어요. 세뇌 당한 가여운 영혼
talk_serena_17503_5.en: That body you call a girl has been taken over by Death himself! Oh poor soul...

talk_serena_17503_6.kr: 승준님! 이 경기만 이기면, 우승이에요! 힘내세요.
talk_serena_17503_6.en: Sam! This is it! This is the finals!

talk_serena_2.en:
I know you because I'm from the future, 
where you're a soccer star!

talk_serena_20.kr:
잠재력이 높은 팀을 찾아 압도적인 실력차이로 
상대를 짓밟아 절망에 빠뜨리고
talk_serena_20.en:
They search for teams with potential, and then obliterate them with brute force, 
making the team fall in despair.

talk_serena_21.kr:
미리 갤럭시 리그에 참가할 경쟁자를 
배제시켜 버리는 자들이죠.
talk_serena_21.en:
In other words, their job is to find 
and eliminate the competition.

talk_serena_22.kr: 그게 바로 방금 승준님이 물리친 자칭 피스메이커.
talk_serena_22.en: And they've just been beaten by you, Sam.

talk_serena_23.en: Well, there's this big soccer league.

talk_serena_24.kr:
전쟁을 막으려는 신들의 수많은 노력 끝에 
더 이상 무력 충돌이 불가능해졌어요.
talk_serena_24.en:
After countless efforts made by the Gods to stop war, 
armed conflict has been completely banned from the universe.

talk_serena_25.kr:
그리고 전쟁 대신 우주의 모든 이권과 분쟁을 
종식시킬 수 있는 절대적인 룰. 단 하나의 규칙.
talk_serena_25.en:
But there still needed to be a method to put an end to conflict, 
so the Galaxy League was born.

talk_serena_26.en: The Galaxy League is the only absolute system there is in the universe.

talk_serena_27.kr:
문제는 그 룰을 악용해 
우주의 섭리를 거스르려는 조직 피스메이커.
talk_serena_27.en:
The only problem with the League is that 
these Peacemakers are trying to use it as a way to control the fate of the universe.

talk_serena_28.kr:
만약 그들이 갤럭시 리그에서 우승한다면, 
우주는 무서운 혼란에 빠질 거에요.
talk_serena_28.en:
If they succeed in winning the Galaxy League, 
chaos will strike the entire universe.

talk_serena_3.kr:
아직은 아니지만, 
엄청난 잠재력을 가지고 계신…
talk_serena_3.en:
Well, not yet apparently, 
but trust me! You'll get there!

talk_serena_32.kr:
하지만, 아직 승준님의 팀은 
리그에 참가하기엔 너무 약해요…
talk_serena_32.en:
But, right now, your team is too weak 
to compete in the Galaxy League.

talk_serena_33.kr:
그러기 위해 시간이 걸리더라도 힘을 키우고, 
무엇보다, 수호자들을 찾으셔야 해요!
talk_serena_33.en:
You need to take time and master your skills. 
And you need to find Guardians to aid you!

talk_serena_34.kr:
네. 수호자들은 피스메이커의 무자비한 도전을
막기위해 전 우주에 흩어져 있어요.
talk_serena_34.en:
Of course. Guardians are sworn protectors. 
They're all around the universe to stop Peacemakers.

talk_serena_35.kr:
결국 축구 전쟁을 근본적으로 막을 방법은 
바로 '우승!'
talk_serena_35.en:
The most fundamental way to prevent war 
is to claim victory.

talk_serena_36.kr:
흩어져 있는 수호자들은 우승을 가져다 줄 
강한 잠재력이 있는 팀에 참가하길 원하고 있어요.
talk_serena_36.en:
Guardians all over the universe all wish 
to join a team with high potential.

talk_serena_37.kr:
아직 승준님의 팀이 약하긴 하지만, 
제가 선택한 분인 만큼 금방 성장할거예요!
talk_serena_37.en:
Your team may be weak right now, 
but I'm sure you'll catch up soon!

talk_serena_38.kr:
그렇게 성장한다면 다른 영웅 분들도 
기꺼이 팀에 합류해 주실거라구요.
talk_serena_38.en:
Once you gain strength, 
others will be more than willing to join your team.

talk_serena_39.kr:
지금은 우선, 동료를 모아 
조금씩 힘을 성장시키는 건 어떨까요?
talk_serena_39.en:
Yes. First, let's start with building up a team. 
Then we can focus on gaining strength.

talk_serena_4.kr:
큐레스씨는 나쁜 사람이 아니에요 승준님. 
명예로운 수호자 중 한 분이랍니다.
talk_serena_4.en:
It's Mr. Cules! 
He's one of the glorious Guardians!

talk_serena_40.kr:
좋아요! 그럼 우선, 
우리 팀부터 함께 정비해봐요!
talk_serena_40.en:
Alright! Then let's start with 
managing the team!

talk_serena_41.en: First, you've got to set the Team Formation.

talk_serena_42.kr:
편성이란, 경기 전에 아군을 자유롭게 
포지션 별로 배치하는 기능입니다.
talk_serena_42.en:
Formation is about putting your Players 
in the right Positions.

talk_serena_44.kr:
잘하셨어요~ 새롭게 나타난 메뉴에서 다시 한번 
편성 버튼을 터치해주세요.
talk_serena_44.en:
Nice! Tap the Formation button once again 
on the new Menu.

talk_serena_45.kr:
지금 보이는 것이 바로 편성 화면이에요. 
우선 화살표가 가리키는 선수를 터치해주세요.
talk_serena_45.en:
The page you're seeing is the Team Formation page. 
Let's start off by tapping the marked Players.

talk_serena_46.kr:
잘하셨어요~ 이렇게 선택한 선수를 
자유롭게 배치할 수 있습니다.
talk_serena_46.en:
Good job! You can switch the position 
of the player to wherever you want!

talk_serena_47.kr:
자동배치 터치하시면 간단하게 
자동으로 배치할 수 있답니다~
talk_serena_47.en:
Tap Auto if you want to have 
your Players placed automatically.

talk_serena_48.kr:
정보보기를 통하여 주력 포지션을 확인하신 후 
배치하시면 더욱 효과적으로 사용하실 수 있어요.
talk_serena_48.en:
Check the best positions for your Players through their Info. 
That's the best place to place them on the field.

talk_serena_49.kr:
단, 우측 상단의 COST를 넘어가면 
편성이 불가능하니 주의해주세요!
talk_serena_49.en: Remember, once it exceeds the COST on the upper right, you won't be able to  put the player in formation.

talk_serena_5.en: Please! You have to listen to me!

talk_serena_50.kr:
지금 당장은 화살표가 가리키는 곳에 
선수를 이동시켜주세요.
talk_serena_50.en:
For now, try moving the Player 
to the designated position.

talk_serena_51.kr:
자, 이번에는 실전 연습을 해볼까요? 
화살표를 따라서 이동해주세요~
talk_serena_51.en:
Time to take it to the field! 
Tap the arrows to follow along.

talk_serena_52.kr:
이곳은 원정 화면입니다. 
스토리모드를 한 번 시작해볼까요?
talk_serena_52.en:
This is the On the Road Menu. 
Let's give Story Mode a try, shall we?

talk_serena_57.kr:
친구가 되면, 친구의 에이스 선수를 이용하여 
경기를 쉽게 풀어갈 수 있답니다.
talk_serena_57.en:
Once you become Friends with another User, you can use 
your Friend's Ace Player to gain an advantage in the match.

talk_serena_58.kr: 자, 이번에 얻은 선수와 함께 훈련을 해볼까요?
talk_serena_58.en: Okay! Now, it's time for some Training!

talk_serena_59.kr:
훈련은 훈련 메뉴를 통해 진행할 수 있어요 
화살표를 선택해주세요.
talk_serena_59.en:
Move to the Training Menu. 
Tap where the arrow is pointing.

talk_serena_6.en:
Accept the challenge, Sam! 
Avenge your friend!

talk_serena_61.kr: 좋아요!~ 이번에는 훈련 할 선수를 선택해주세요.
talk_serena_61.en: Well done! Now choose the Player you'd like to Train.

talk_serena_63.en: Now choose the Player you'd like to use as material.

talk_serena_64.kr: 모두 함께 힘을 모아서… 훈련…… 시작~!

talk_serena_65.en: Splendid! The Player's Level and Stats have increased!

talk_serena_66.en: That's all there is to Training.

talk_serena_69.en: It's time for us to meet our Team Manager.

talk_serena_7.kr: 저 자는 지금 갤럭시 리그 토너먼트를 제안했어요.
talk_serena_7.en: That man just challenged you to a Galaxy League Tournament!

talk_serena_74.kr: 매니저 스킬 사용에는 각자 일정 시간이 필요해요.
talk_serena_74.en: Manager Skills all require some time to be used.

talk_serena_75.kr: 매니저의 종류마다 배치할 수 있는 위치가 다르다는 점도 기억해두세요!
talk_serena_75.en: Remember, the place you can station your Manager differs according to the type.

talk_serena_76.en: Fantastic! I knew you could do it!

talk_serena_77.kr: 우승 기념으로 프리 매치에 대해 알려드릴게요~ 제가 표시하는 것을 잘 따라 해보세요~
talk_serena_77.en: As a gift, let me tell you guys about the Free Match! Watch and follow!

talk_serena_78.en: This right here is the Bonus Mission!

talk_serena_79.kr: 한 번 클리어한 리그는 다시 도전할 수가 있는데 여기에 보너스 미션으로 다양한 보상을 제공하고 있답니다~
talk_serena_79.en: You can re-play the Leagues you've already won. But when you re-play, you'll be provided with Bonus Missions that come with various Rewards!

talk_serena_8.kr:
제가 승준님에게 출전권을 부여했어요! 
자, 가요~ 승준님! 이기는 거에요!
talk_serena_8.en:
I let them sign you up! 
Now go! Go beat them!

talk_serena_80.kr: 뭐, 선택적인 부분이라 리그매치만 진행하셔도 상관없어요~
talk_serena_80.en: It's optional, so you don't have to do it if you don't want to.

talk_serena_81.kr: 그럼 이쯤에서 마지막으로 선수 뽑기에 대해 알려 드릴께요~
talk_serena_81.en: Finally, allow me to introduce you to the Player Draw system.

talk_serena_83.kr: 자~ 여기가 뽑기 화면이에요 유료로 레어 선수 뽑기와 친구와의 우정을 모아 뽑는 우정 선수 뽑기가 있답니다~
talk_serena_83.en: This is the Draw page. You can either Draw Players by using Crystals or FP.

talk_serena_84.kr: 우선은 제가 가진 시공석으로 선수를 한 명 찾아볼게요
talk_serena_84.en: Let's try drawing a player with the Crystals I've got.

talk_serena_85.kr: 이건 '시공석'이라고 해요. 게임플레이를 통해 얻을 수도 있고 상점에서도 판매하고 있어요.
talk_serena_85.en: These are Crystals. You can get them by playing the game or buy them at the Store.

talk_serena_87.kr:
여기까지 오시느라 대단히 수고 많으셨어요. 
이제 남은 건 갤럭시 리그를 향해 최고의 팀을 만드는 것뿐!
talk_serena_87.en:
Well, that's all I have to teach you about. 
Now you're on your own!

talk_serena_88.kr:
지금까지 배운 것을 기억하시고, 
본격적으로 우승을 향해 함께 힘내보아요~ 파이팅!
talk_serena_88.en:
Remember what you've learned today, build up a good team, 
and become the champion of the Galaxy Universe!

talk_serena_9.en: This is what I've been trying to explain to you back there!

talk_seungjun_1.en: Time to get back to training!

talk_seungjun_10203_10.kr: 우린 우주로 나갈 방법이 없는걸? 세레나, 너 우주선이라도 가지고 있는 거야?
talk_seungjun_10203_10.en: But wait. We don't have the means to go to outer space. Do you have something like a space ship?

talk_seungjun_10203_2.kr: 세레나, 이제 네 말처럼 지구에 평화가 오는 거야?
talk_seungjun_10203_2.en: Selena, does this mean that we've brought peace to Earth like you said?

talk_seungjun_10203_4.en: That Youth League wasn't the end of it?

talk_seungjun_10203_7.kr: 외…외계인과 축구를 한다는 말인 거야? 다리 넷이고 막 그런?
talk_seungjun_10203_7.en: Did you really mean it when you talked about playing soccer against aliens and stuff?

talk_seungjun_10301_12.en: What? You asked for it! I'm bringing in everything I've got!

talk_seungjun_10301_2_4.kr: 내가 만나야 하는 자들이 있는 거야?

talk_seungjun_10301_4.kr: 자랑할 때가 아니라구, 지구엔 어떻게 돌아가냐구우~
talk_seungjun_10301_4.en: How in the world am I supposed to get back?

talk_seungjun_10502_2_5.kr: (그런 건 미리 말해주지. 얼마나 힘들었는지 알아? 칫!)
talk_seungjun_10502_2_5.en: You know, a little heads up could have been useful...

talk_seungjun_10502_2_7.en: Anyways...Get ready. We're up for the next match!

talk_seungjun_10502_2_8.en: I'm starting to get curious about this Galaxy League.

talk_seungjun_11.kr:
무… 무슨 리그? 난 그런 거 들어본 적도 없어! 
참가 신청 같은 건 안했다구!
talk_seungjun_11.en:
Galaxy what? I never signed up for that! 
I've never even heard of it!

talk_seungjun_11101_10.kr: 뭐? 그건 마치… 신이 되는 것 같잖아?

talk_seungjun_11101_15.en: ...Thanks for the explanation. But again, a little heads up please?

talk_seungjun_11101_2.kr: 세레나 네가 말한 우주 최고의 리그가 바로 여기로군?
talk_seungjun_11101_2.en: This is the most prestigious League throughout the universe, right?

talk_seungjun_11101_4.kr: 그런데 갤럭시 리그에 우승하면… 뭐가 좋은 거야?
talk_seungjun_11101_4.en: But why is this Galaxy League such a big deal?

talk_seungjun_11103_1.kr: 행성 리그와는 또 다르군. 후. 이제 마지막 한 경기만 이기면!!
talk_seungjun_11103_1.en: The games here are much tougher than the Planetary Leagues! One more game to win!

talk_seungjun_11103_2_3.en: Vengence, huh? Just make sure they follow the rules, okay?

talk_seungjun_11103_6.kr: 크루젠테스..? 아. 그 거칠었던 행성 말인가?
talk_seungjun_11103_6.en: Cruzentes? Oh that planet with rough terrain...

talk_seungjun_11703_10.en: Tod! Buddy! What are you doing over there?

talk_seungjun_11703_16.en: I accept that as a challenge!

talk_seungjun_11703_2_2.kr: 아직 늦지 않았다. 박태호. 돌아온다면 받아주겠어.
talk_seungjun_11703_2_2.en: It's not too late Tod. Come back, buddy.

talk_seungjun_11703_4.kr: 이그드라실 수호대..? 멋들어진 이름이네. 근데 왜?
talk_seungjun_11703_4.en: Yggdrasil Guardians? Cool name. What about it?

talk_seungjun_11703_8.kr: 요즘 안 보인다 싶더니… 이게 어떻게 된 일이지?
talk_seungjun_11703_8.en: I haven't seen him in a while...What happened?

talk_seungjun_12.kr:
뭐… 뭐라구?!!?! 
그런걸 맘대로 가능해? 내 동의도 없이???
talk_seungjun_12.en:
Hey wait! What?! How... 
Do you even have the authority? What about my consent?

talk_seungjun_12301_10.kr: 잘 모르는 사람이랑 한 팀을 하고 싶진 않아!
talk_seungjun_12301_10.en: No! Why would I? And who'd want to be in a team of strangers?

talk_seungjun_12301_2.en: And you are? Are you the manager of the team we're going against?

talk_seungjun_12301_23.en: What? Who said anything about that?

talk_seungjun_12301_2_10.en: They just came out of nowhere!

talk_seungjun_12301_2_17.en: You know, this would have been much easier if you said that in the first place.

talk_seungjun_12301_2_19.kr: 뭐, 좋아. 나중에 어찌 되든 일단 같이 뛰어보지.

talk_seungjun_12903_1.en: We're close to winning this League too!

talk_seungjun_12903_12.kr: 웃기지 마시지! 선의의 경쟁 외에 다른 룰은 없다는 걸 알 텐데?
talk_seungjun_12903_12.en: Wow, after all those stories about angels, who'd knew they'd really be like this!

talk_seungjun_12903_2_11.kr: 미래라는 곳에서? 난 뭘 하게 되지?
talk_seungjun_12903_2_11.en: You said you've came from the future. What do I do there?

talk_seungjun_12903_2_7.kr: 내가 뭘 했다고 저러는 거지? 세레나.
talk_seungjun_12903_2_7.en: Selena, tell me. Did I do something wrong?

talk_seungjun_13.kr:
하지만 그런 알지도 못하는 리그에 
내가 출전할 리 없잖아!
talk_seungjun_13.en:
Stop with this nonsense! I don't even know about this league! 
Why would I be playing in it?

talk_seungjun_13503_2_1.en: Wow, we won...But that was close...

talk_seungjun_13503_2_3.kr: 이걸 축구라고 불러야 해? 너희! 반칙이나 하고
talk_seungjun_13503_2_3.en: This isn't soccer! Hey! That was a foul back there!

talk_seungjun_13503_7.kr: 상대하지 말고 승부나 하자. 악마들은 꽤 시끄럽고 피곤하군.
talk_seungjun_13503_7.en: Just ignore him. Let's focus on the game. Man he's so annoying.

talk_seungjun_14103_1.kr: 박태호!! 널 여기서 또 보다니? 어떻게 된 거지?
talk_seungjun_14103_1.en: Tod! I didn't expect to see you here again. What are you doing here?

talk_seungjun_14103_2_6.kr: 하지만 쉽진 않았어. 상대팀 역시 점점 강해지니까.
talk_seungjun_14103_2_6.en: But it wasn't easy. The competition is getting tougher every step up the ladder.

talk_seungjun_14702_2.en: Who is it? We're about to start another match you know.

talk_seungjun_14702_2_1.kr: 내 승리야! 이젠 인정할 수 있겠어?
talk_seungjun_14702_2_1.en: You lost! Now can you admit her choice?

talk_seungjun_14702_2_11.en: What's all this about you being a prophet?

talk_seungjun_14702_2_13.kr: 내가 승리하는 건 네 덕이란 말이야?
talk_seungjun_14702_2_13.en: Are you saying that I keep on winning because of you?

talk_seungjun_14702_2_9.kr: 아직도 넌 비밀 투성이군. 날 믿는 거야? 믿지 못하는 거야?
talk_seungjun_14702_2_9.en: More secrets. How can I trust you?

talk_seungjun_14702_4.en: Vermilion Bird? You mean Vermilion Bird of the Katrina Association?

talk_seungjun_15.kr:
자격 상실? 그딴 리그 안 나가면 되는 거잖아! 
이렇게 갑자기 쳐들어 와선…
talk_seungjun_15.en:
Lose our right? I'd be glad if we didn't even start in the first place! 
I'm still confused, this is all so sudden!

talk_seungjun_15302_1.en: This place looks mystical. What is this place?

talk_seungjun_15302_2_1.en: How's that! Have you got anything to say?

talk_seungjun_15302_3.kr: 와~ 여기선 공 차면 안될 것 같은 분위긴데?
talk_seungjun_15302_3.en: Can we really play soccer here? I get the feeling we're not supposed to.

talk_seungjun_15302_7.kr: 날 무시하다니… 그런 소리 못하게 만들어주지!!
talk_seungjun_15302_7.en: I'll show you that we're worthy enough to compete in the League!

talk_seungjun_15903_2.kr: 천상의 축구? 그건 뭐 다른 건가?
talk_seungjun_15903_2.en: Isn't soccer still soccer in heaven?

talk_seungjun_16.kr:
말도 안 되는 말 하지마! 
그런 이야기를 나보러 믿으라는 거야?!
talk_seungjun_16.en:
Stop it! 
You can't just think that I'd believe everything you say!

talk_seungjun_16502_11.kr: 그게 더 불안하다고! 술은 마셨지만 음주운전은 안 한거랑 뭐가 다른 건데?
talk_seungjun_16502_11.en: That's what makes it more frightening!

talk_seungjun_16502_2_2.kr: 크윽… 이기긴 했는데, 피해가 너무 크군…
talk_seungjun_16502_2_2.en: We did win...but look that the damage...

talk_seungjun_16502_2_3.kr: 이런 악당 같은 놈! 일부러 그런 거지!
talk_seungjun_16502_2_3.en: You! You did all of this on purpose!

talk_seungjun_16502_7.kr: 야! 정말 저런 녀석을 내보내겠다고? 제정신이야?
talk_seungjun_16502_7.en: Hey! Are you seriously going to let this guy play?

talk_seungjun_16502_9.en: Did you hear what he just said? Is it even okay to let a criminal out on the fields?

talk_seungjun_17103_2_7.en: What a coincidence. I'm frightened of you, devil!

talk_seungjun_17503_2_1.en: Yes! Yes! I won the Galaxy League!

talk_seungjun_17503_2_10.kr: 윽, 이건 꼭 내가 울린 것 같잖아?
talk_seungjun_17503_2_10.en: Uh oh...She's about to cry. There, there. It's alright.

talk_seungjun_17503_2_3.kr: 그래. 노아 네가 없었으면 불가능했을 거야.
talk_seungjun_17503_2_3.en: Oh, yes. Without you, this would've been impossible.

talk_seungjun_17503_4.kr: 이렇게 연약한 소녀와도 전투해야 하는 건가?
talk_seungjun_17503_4.en: Now I have to play against a little girl?

talk_seungjun_18.kr:
도대체 무슨 말 하는지 하나도 모르겠지만, 
너희들! 그렇게까지 말한다면…
talk_seungjun_18.en:
I really have no idea  
what you guys are talking about. But...

talk_seungjun_19.en: I won't just stand here like a fool.

talk_seungjun_2.kr:
뭐… 뭐야? 당신. 
왜 내 이름을 아는 거지?
talk_seungjun_2.en:
Who? What? 
Who are you and how do you know me?

talk_seungjun_21.kr: 그런 기본적인 것도 내가 모를것 같아?

talk_seungjun_22.kr:
골을 넣으면 이기는 건 당연하잖아!... 
 … 뭐??? 한 골 만에 끝난다구?
talk_seungjun_22.en:
Of course you win when you score... 
Wait. Did you just say one goal?

talk_seungjun_24.en: This is soccer we're playing, right?

talk_seungjun_25.en: I don't like this at all...

talk_seungjun_28.en: ...I have no idea what you're talking about.

talk_seungjun_29.kr:
… 잠깐 지금 너, 
우주에서 왔다고 말하는 거야?

talk_seungjun_3.kr:
훗. 뭐 그렇지. 
난 세계 챔피언이 될 몸이니까!
talk_seungjun_3.en:
You got that right! 
I'll get there someday!

talk_seungjun_30.kr: 지금, 내가 믿을 거라고 말하는 거야?
talk_seungjun_30.en: You're making this all up right?

talk_seungjun_32.en: I am the one to stop the universe from trouble?

talk_seungjun_36.kr:
수호자? 아까 그 덩치? 
그런 덩치가 한 명이 아니었던 거야?
talk_seungjun_36.en:
Guardians? Oh that big fella back there? 
There's more like him?

talk_seungjun_38.en: The High School League starts soon...

talk_seungjun_39.en: I guess that would be a good place to start. Let's win it!

talk_seungjun_4.kr:
하지만 내 이름을 아는 당신이나, 
저렇게 무서운 덩치가 부르다니. 누가 봐도 이상하잖아?
talk_seungjun_4.en:
But back to my question. Who are you guys? 
What do you and Mr. Gargantuan want from me?

talk_seungjun_43.kr: 자~ 이제 좀 강해진 거 같으니 다음 경기를 진행해볼까?
talk_seungjun_43.en: Now that the team has gotten a little stronger, let's move on to the next Match!

talk_seungjun_44.en: Coach? When did you come here?

talk_seungjun_45.en: Counter attack, guys! Pass the ball!

talk_seungjun_47.kr: 괜찮아! 우리가 여고라고 너무 얕본 것 같아.
talk_seungjun_47.en: Stop blaming yourself. We underestimated the other team because they're new.

talk_seungjun_51.kr: 매니저? 그… 수건 들고 땀 닦아주는 귀여운 여고생 말이지?

talk_seungjun_55.kr: 역시 저 녀석들 너무 강해 보이는데? 괜찮겠어?
talk_seungjun_55.en: Wow, they look tough. Think you'll be alright?

talk_seungjun_55_1.en: Ryle! I'll leave it up to you! Take care of them!

talk_seungjun_56.en: Nice Pass! I won't miss this opportunity!

talk_seungjun_58.en: So this thing just keeps on going...

talk_seungjun_6.kr:
역시 수상하잖아!
난 훈련 중이니 방해하지 말라구~
talk_seungjun_6.en:
Hercules? Guardian? 
Give me a break! I'm going to go train.

talk_seungjun_7.kr:
어라? 운동장에서 경기가?
날 빼고 연습경기 중인 건가??
talk_seungjun_7.en:
Hmm? A match without me? 
Come on guys! Without me? Really?

talk_seungjun_8.en:
Ryle? Buddy what's wrong?! 
You're...You're injured!

talk_sorang_10301_9.en: No fur! You must be Human!

talk_sute_1_1.kr:
신화여고 축구팀은 올해 창설되었습니다.
전력을 알 수 없으니 주의하시길…
talk_sute_1_1.en:
The Legend Women's High School soccer team's pretty new to the league.
There's not a lot of information on them, so please be careful.

talk_sute_2.en: Miss Noa. It's been a while.

talk_sute_3.kr:
사정은 들었습니다.
악에 맞서 싸우신다니 그 용기에 감복했습니다.
talk_sute_3.en:
I've heard the story. 
Fighting against evil. I am very impressed.

talk_sute_4.kr: 자, 이곳이 훈련소입니다. 생각보다 크고 아름다워 놀랐습니다만, 맡겨주십시오.
talk_sute_4.en: This is the Training Facility. It's bigger and more beautiful than I thought, but there's nothing I can't handle.

talk_sute_5.en: Now before anything else, register me as your Manager.

talk_sute_6.kr:
좋습니다. 이제 제 능력 '완벽주의자'가 발동합니다.
제가 있는 한 모든 선수의 피지컬이 증가할겁니다.
talk_sute_6.en:
Good. Now my Skill Perfectionist will be in effect. 
As long as you have me as your Manager, all your Players will have increased Physical Stats.

talk_sute_7.kr: 추가로 강력한 액션도 취할 수 있지만 당장은 어렵겠군요.
talk_sute_7.en: I'm capable of more, but I'm not quite ready yet.

talk_suzy_1.kr: 걱정 마~ 빼앗기를 사용해서 적이 쓰러지면 다시 공을 뺏을 수 있어!
talk_suzy_1.en: Take the enemy down with Steal and get the ball!

talk_suzy_10.en: I guess our only option is to go for the Long Pass!

talk_suzy_3.kr: 얘들아~ 아직 끝난 게 아냐! 리그는 3경기 중 2경기를 승리해도 우승할 수 있어~
talk_suzy_3.en: Um, hey guys? It's not over yet. We still have a chance at winning this League if we win the next Match.

talk_suzy_4.kr: 에휴~ 그런 기초적인 것도 몰랐단 말이야?
talk_suzy_4.en: Come on guys! This is basic stuff!

talk_suzy_5.kr:
리그는 4개팀이 풀 리그로 진행되니까,
마지막 한 경기를 이겨서 우승을 노려보자!
talk_suzy_5.en:
Each League has 4 Teams competing, 
so if we win the last Match, we still have a chance.

talk_suzy_6.kr: 게다가 다른 팀이 이미 1패씩 했기 때문에 다음 경기를 이기면 우승할 수 있다구~!
talk_suzy_6.en: The other teams all lost 1 game each. There's plenty of room for us to get back into the game.

talk_suzy_7.kr: 자~ 그럼 감독님도 도와주시니까 다음 경기는 반드시 이겨보자구~
talk_suzy_7.en: Now that we have a coach on our bench, let's go win the next Match!

talk_suzy_9.en: We've got to get the ball to Sam!

talk_taeho_11703_11.en: I'm sorry it's got to be like this.

talk_taeho_11703_12.kr: 이그드라실 수호대는 태어난 행성과 관계 없는 집단. 이곳에서는 내 실력을 펼칠 수 있는 곳이었어.
talk_taeho_11703_12.en: There are no limits in the Yggdrasil Guardians. Here I can prove myself worthy only with my skills.

talk_taeho_11703_13.kr: 늘… 네 뒤에만 있을 순 없었다. 강승준.
talk_taeho_11703_13.en: I can't always hide in your shadow, Sam...

talk_taeho_11703_2_10.kr: 그렇다. 이 은하의 균형을 위한 의지로 탄생한 구단이지.
talk_taeho_11703_2_10.en: That's right. This team is devoted to protect the balance of the universe.

talk_taeho_11703_2_11.kr: 나는 이 곳에 머물 거다. 강승준.
talk_taeho_11703_2_11.en: This is where I belong, Sam.

talk_taeho_11703_2_3.kr: 그럴 순 없어. 팀을 정비해 언젠가, 너와 승부할거다.
talk_taeho_11703_2_3.en: I can't. No, I won't. I'm going to rebuild the team. And I'm going to challenge you again, Sam.

talk_taeho_11703_2_5.kr: 난, 갤럭시 리그를 알고 있었다. 강승준
talk_taeho_11703_2_5.en: I knew about the Galaxy League, Sam.

talk_taeho_11703_2_6.kr: 세레나양이 나타났을 때, 너희 팀에 합류하면 이 갤럭시 리그에 참가할 수 있을 거라 생각했지.
talk_taeho_11703_2_6.en: The moment Selena came to us back on Earth, I thought the glorious role would be mine!

talk_taeho_11703_2_7.kr: 하지만 모든 빛은 네게만 주어졌다. 세레나양이 너를 믿는 한 내게 에이스의 기회는 오지 않아.
talk_taeho_11703_2_7.en: But no...It had to be you. With you around, I knew that I would never become the ace of the team.

talk_taeho_11703_2_8.kr: 그걸 깨달았다. 내 뜻을 펼칠 수 있는 곳을 찾았을 뿐.
talk_taeho_11703_2_8.en: So I had to make a decision, and that's when I found out about this team.

talk_taeho_14103_2.kr: 리그는 계속 되고 있다고. 설마, 한번 이기면 두 번 다시 안 볼 거라 생각한 거야?
talk_taeho_14103_2.en: This is a League, not a Tournament. Of course you'd be seeing me again.

talk_taeho_14103_5.en: Yes it is. And this time I'll win!

talk_vergil_14103_10.en: I'll make sure that you never get up again.

talk_vergil_14103_2_2.en: I just bought this suit yesterday...

talk_vergil_14103_2_4.en: Hmph! We'll see how things go next time.

talk_vergil_14103_4.en: Is it him? The one that defeated you?

talk_vergil_14103_6.kr: 당연한 소릴! 나와 함께하는 한 패배는 없다.
talk_vergil_14103_6.en: With me by your side, defeat is not an option.

talk_vergil_14103_8.en: You can talk. I can see that.

talk_vergil_14103_9.en: You're up against me this time, Sam.

talk_wayne_1.kr: 뭘 망설여? 빼앗기로 적의 체력을 떨어뜨리면 빼앗을 수 있다구.
talk_wayne_1.en: What are you waiting for? Lower their HP with Steal!

talk_wayne_3.kr: 하지만 한 경기가 더 있어, 아직 우승 희망은 있다는 얘기지.
talk_wayne_3.en: Well, if we win the last Match, we still have hope to win the League.

talk_wayne_4.en: I'm surprised that you didn't know.

talk_wayne_5.kr:
리그는 4개팀이 풀 리그로 진행되니까,
지금 마지막 경기 결과가 아직 남았고
talk_wayne_5.en:
The league has 4 teams competing on a Full League. 
We have one game left, and so do the others.

talk_wayne_6.kr: 다른 팀이 이미 1패씩 했기 때문에 다음 경기만 이기면 우승할 수 있잖아.
talk_wayne_6.en: All the other teams have 1 lost match each. This means if we win the next Match, we still have a shot at winning.

talk_wayne_7.kr: 다음 경기는 열풍고교야. 슬슬 재미있어 지겠는걸?
talk_wayne_7.en: Next up is Gale High School. Should be fun.

talk_wejol_1.kr: 수호자? 흥! 웬 벌레 한 마리가 끼어들었군.
talk_wejol_1.en: What do we have here? A Guardian? Ha!

talk_wejol_2.en: No! We can't lose like this!

talk_wejol_3.kr:
어떻게 보고하지? 
지구에 오자마자 벌써 져버리다니!
talk_wejol_3.en:
How am I supposed to report this? 
Lose as soon as I get to Earth?

talk_wejol_5.kr: 이상한 꼬마녀석이? 이거 계획에는 없던 일인데? 괜찮을까?

talk_wejol_6.kr: 꼬맹이들 천국이로군. 난 꼬맹이들이 좋더라 히히히
talk_wejol_6.en: They're all kids! Ha, this should be easy.

talk_wejol_7.en: No! We can't lose like this!

talk_wejol_8.kr:
어떻게 보고하지? 
지구에 오자마자 벌써 져버리다니!
talk_wejol_8.en:
How am I supposed to report this? 
Lose as soon as I get to Earth?

ui_advice_spirit_arousal.kr: 강화 3단계마다 일정 확률로 동일한 문양 및 속성의 한 단계 위 스톤으로 진화할 수 있습니다.
ui_advice_spirit_arousal.en: The Spirit Stone can Evolve with a fixed chance to a higher grade Spirit Stone with the same symbol and attribute for every 3rd Power-up level.

ui_advice_spirit_change.kr: 스피릿 스톤을 획득하거나, 강화 3단계가 될 때마다 랜덤한 능력의 추가 옵션을 최대 5개 획득 가능합니다.
ui_advice_spirit_change.en: The Spirit Stone can get up to 5 bonus properties for every 3rd Power-up level or when you get the Spirit Stone.

ui_advice_spirit_equip.kr: 속성 슬롯은 동일 속성의 스톤만 장착 할 수 있습니다. (특별 훈련으로 열리는 프리즘 슬롯은 제외)
ui_advice_spirit_equip.en: You can only equip stones of the same attribute in attribute slots. (Prism slots available from Special Training excluded)

ui_advice_spirit_sell.kr: 사용하지 않는 스피릿 스톤은 골드로 판매 가능합니다. (다중 선택으로 최대 12개 선택이 가능하며, 일괄 판매 가능)
ui_advice_spirit_sell.en: You can sell unwanted Spirit Stones for Gold. (You can sell up to 12 stones at once.)

ui_advice_spirit_strengthen.kr:
골드를 소모하여 강화 시도를 합니다.
확률에 따라 성공 시 강화 단계가 올라가며 스피릿 스톤 능력치가 향상됩니다.
네리스를 사용하여 확정강화가 가능합니다.
ui_advice_spirit_strengthen.en:
You can consume Gold to Power-up.
The Power-up level and the Spirit Stone stats will increase by chance.
You can use a Neris to guarantee success of the Power-up.

ui_ch_recall_notice_unequipstone.en: You can't make a recall if the subject character is equipped with Spirit Stones.

ui_ch_recall_policy_info1.kr: 밸런싱 패치 또는 버그 수정, 개발 사이드 이펙트 등의 요인으로 캐릭터의 가치가 현저하게 감소했다고 판단되는 경우 리콜 대상으로 선정될 수 있습니다.
ui_ch_recall_policy_info1.en: A character may be selected as a recallable player if the character's value has significantly decreased due to balancing patches, bug fixes, development side effects, etc.

ui_ch_recall_policy_info2.kr: 리콜 대상으로 선정되면 게임 내 공지를 통해 리콜이 진행될 캐릭터와 기간을 안내받을 수 있습니다.
ui_ch_recall_policy_info2.en:
If a character has been selected as a recallable character,
you will be notified about the character and recall period through an in-game notice.

ui_ch_recall_policy_info3.kr: 리콜은 리콜이 진행되는 기간동안 1회만 실행할 수 있습니다.
ui_ch_recall_policy_info3.en: You can only use the recall function once during the recall period.

ui_ch_recall_policy_info4.kr: 리콜 캐릭터는 리콜을 실행하면 동일한 육성 경험치, 특별훈련 단계, +강화 수치, 클로버 수치를 이전할 수 있는 대체 캐릭터를 생성합니다.
ui_ch_recall_policy_info4.en:
When making a recall, you will receive a character that has inherited the EXP, Special Training value,
Powered-up status, and Clover value of the recalled character.

ui_ch_recall_policy_info5.kr: 대체 캐릭터는 등급에 맞는 캐릭터에게만 훈련 재료로 사용이 가능하며, 재료로 사용 시 대체 캐릭터가 가진 효과가 더해집니다.
ui_ch_recall_policy_info5.en:
The substitute character can be used as power-up material for characters with legitimate grade,
and the inherited statuses will be transferred to the powered-up character.

ui_ch_recall_policy_info6.kr: 대체 캐릭터로 이전되는 경험치, 특별훈련 단계, +강화 수치, 클로버 수치는 그 최대치를 넘기지 않습니다.
ui_ch_recall_policy_info6.en: The EXP, Special Training, Power-up, and Clover related values transferred from the substitute character can't make those status of the subject character exceed their maximum limits.

ui_ch_recall_result_info2.kr: 리콜로 교환된 쇼쇼는 숙소로, GP는 우편으로 지급되었습니다.
ui_ch_recall_result_info2.en: Sho Sho has been sent to your Lodging, and the GP has been sent to your inbox.

ui_ch_recall_reward_info.kr:
다른 캐릭터에 훈련재료로 사용 시 경험치, 초월강화, 클로버, +강화를 강화 대상에게 추가로 더해줍니다.
(최대치 이상 증가하지 않음) 특별훈련은 강화 대상과 비교해 높은 경우 덮어씁니다.
초월단계는 쇼쇼 본체를 제외한 순수 초월단계만 더해집니다.
ui_ch_recall_reward_info.en:
Adds other power-up effects(EXP, Superb Power-up, Clover, or Power-up Levels) when used as material to power-up other characters, but doesn't have any effect if the power-up type is at its max level.
When using Sho Sho for Special Training material, the higher value will be granted to the subject character.

ui_match_ui_league_description.en: Win a League to be promoted to the next League.

ui_match_ui_space_blackhole.kr: 승리하면 100% 확률로 블랙홀 뿌우를 얻을 수 있습니다.(매니저를 통한 추가 획득은 불가능) 매 주 1회만 클리어 가능합니다.

ui_match_ui_space_boss.kr: 승리하면 일정 확률로 4성 라이벌을 얻을 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_boss.en: You can get a 4-Star rival with a fixed chance if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_event.en: You can get an event character with a fixed chance if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_fool.kr: 승리하면 일정 확률로 기획서를 획득할 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_fool.en: You may get a Development Plan by chance when you clear the Match.

ui_match_ui_space_guerrilla.kr: 승리하면 대량의 경험치를 가진 펭귄을 얻을 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_guerrilla.en: You can get a penguin with a great amount of EXP if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_limit.kr: 승리하면 특별한 보상을 얻을 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_limit.en: You'll get special rewards when you win.

ui_match_ui_space_limit_fire.kr: 승리하면 100% 확률로 불꽃 펭귄 대장을 획득할 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_limit_fire.en: You can get the Fire Penguin Leader with a 100% chance if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_limit_saturday.kr: 승리하면 많은 경험치를 획득할 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_limit_saturday.en: You can get lots of EXP if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_limit_sunday.kr: 승리하면 많은 골드를 획득할 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_limit_sunday.en: You can get lots of Gold if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_quest.kr: 퀘스트 매치를 클리어하면 100% 확률로 해당 보상을 획득할 수 있습니다. 실패해도 횟수가 차감되지 않습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_quest.en: You are guaranteed to get the reward when you clear a Quest Match. Chances will not be deducted even if you fail.

ui_match_ui_space_rainbow.kr: 승리하면 100% 확률로 무지개 정령을 얻을 수 있습니다.(매니저를 통한 추가 획득은 불가능) 매 주 1회만 클리어 가능합니다.
ui_match_ui_space_rainbow.en: You can get the Rainbow Elemental with a 100% chance if you win. (Can't get additional Rainbow Elementals through managers.) You can clear this match only once per week.

ui_match_ui_space_real_boss.kr: 승리하면 일정 확률로 5성 보스를 얻을 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_real_boss.en: You can get a 5-Star Boss with a fixed chance if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_transcendence_boss.kr: 승리하면 100% 확률로 초월보스를 획득할 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_transcendence_boss.en: You can get a Superb Boss with a 100% chance if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_transcendence_buff_con.kr:
※ 초월보스 탈력이란?

초월보스에서 일정 횟수 패배 시 적 전체에게 디버프를 걸어 해당 매치의 난이도가 점차적으로 낮아지게 됩니다.(적 전체 디버프는 중첩으로 쌓이게 됩니다.)
ui_match_ui_space_transcendence_buff_con.en:
※What's the Superb Boss's Enervation?

A weakening effect will be cast on all enemies if you continuously fail to clear the Super Boss match. This weakening effect accumulates and drops the difficulty.

ui_match_ui_space_weekday.kr: 승리하면 일정 확률로 각성 재료를 얻을 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_weekday.en: You can get Evolution materials with a fixed chance if you win.

ui_match_ui_space_weekend.kr: 승리하면 많은 골드와 일정 확률로 강화용 뿌우를 얻을 수 있습니다.
ui_match_ui_space_weekend.en: You can get lots of Gold and Swirly for Power-ups with a fixed chance if you win.

ui_match_weather_eff_2.en: Decreases the support skill effect of all players by 75%.

ui_match_weather_eff_3.kr: 모든 선수 받는 회복 효과 75% 감소
ui_match_weather_eff_3.en: Decreases the HP recovery of all players by 75%.

ui_match_weather_eff_4.kr: 모든 선수 매 1분 마다 체력 5% 감소
ui_match_weather_eff_4.en: Decreases the HP of all players by 5% every 1 min.

ui_method_evolution.kr: 각성 재료를 모았을 시 레벨에 관계없이 각성 가능합니다. 각성한 선수는 모든 능력치가 크게 증가하며 새로운 스킬을 습득합니다.

ui_method_upgrade.kr: 선수 훈련을 통해 빠르게 레벨업이 가능합니다. 20레벨 부터는 스페이스 펭귄 등의 특수 카드를 통해 훈련하면 더욱 효율적입니다.

ui_pull_tg_info1.kr: 이벤트 뽑기 44회 안에 5성 이상 선수 최소 한 명을 획득할 수 있도록 보정하는 시스템입니다.
ui_pull_tg_info1.en: This is a system to ensure at least one 5 star or up draw within 44 Event Draws.

ui_pull_tg_info2.kr: 이벤트 뽑기 시도 시 5성 이상 선수를 획득하지 못할 경우 게이지는 누적이 되고, 꽉 찰 경우 다음 이벤트 뽑기에서 5성 이상 선수를 확정 획득 할 수 있습니다.
ui_pull_tg_info2.en: If you fail to acquire a 5 star or higher player through the event draw, the gauge will fill up. When the gauge becomes fully filled up, your next event draw will ensure a 5 Star or higher draw, and the gauge will reset.

ui_pull_tg_info3.kr: 5성 이상 선수를 획득했을 때 게이지는 초기화 됩니다.
ui_pull_tg_info3.en: The gauge will reset when you get a 5 star or higher player.

ui_pull_tg_info4.kr: 10+1회 뽑기 중 5성 이상의 선수를 획득한 경우, 마지막으로 획득한 5성 이상의 선수를 기점으로 게이지는 초기화되고, 다시 누적됩니다.
ui_pull_tg_info4.en: If you acquire a 5 star or higher player during the 10+1 draw, the gauge will reset and start filling up from the point you've acquired a 5 star or higher player.

ui_pull_tg_info5.kr: 무료 뽑기 시도 및 프리미엄 티켓 사용 시에도 게이지는 누적됩니다.
ui_pull_tg_info5.en: The gauge also fills up when you do a free draw or use a premium ticket.

ui_pull_tg_info6.kr: 우정 뽑기 및 우정 무료 뽑기는 이벤트 뽑기 보정 시스템에 영향을 주지 않습니다.
